Estaba esto en gamedev.net, por ahi ya lo conocian...

$45,000 grand prize value for your Java Game
Posted by: CaptainJester at 07:35	
There is a new Java game coding contest over at Sun's Java Gaming website. 
Here is an excerpt:

Calling all independent video game developers! Have you developed a cool 
video game using Java technology? If so, enter it in the 2004 Java 
Technology Game Development Contest and compete for $50,000 in prizes! The 
entry period begins March 23, 2004 and runs through June 7, 2004 at 9:00am 
Pacific Time

Check it out at https://games-contest.dev.java.net/


Gabriel.
